## Limitations

The report is based on available data and articles up to April 2025. The dynamic nature of global oil markets and economic policies means that new developments could further influence petrol prices. Additionally, the report relies on secondary sources, which may not capture all nuances of the factors affecting petrol prices. Further primary research and data analysis would be required for a more comprehensive understanding.

